rows.label: qst202409_msg0001
rows.name: Isn't that Countess Omulette?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0002
rows.name:
Looks like it.
She certainly fits the description.

rows.label: qst202409_msg0003
rows.name:
But she doesn't look very kidnapped.
She looks like she's enjoying herself.

rows.label: qst202409_msg0004
rows.name:
Well that's strange. Maybe
it's not her after all.

rows.label: qst202409_msg0005
rows.name: Let's just go over and see!

rows.label: qst202409_msg0006
rows.name:
Good idea. Let's see what
she has to say.

rows.label: qst202409_msg0007
rows.name: Are you the Countess Omulette?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0008
rows.name: And you are?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0009
rows.name:
One of your people sent
us to rescue you.

rows.label: qst202409_msg0010
rows.name: Rescue? Me?!

rows.label: qst202409_msg0011
rows.name:
But you don't appear to be in danger.
What's going on?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0012
rows.name: Craa craa...

rows.label: qst202409_msg0013
rows.name: Why am here again?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0014
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0015
rows.name: You...forgot?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0016
rows.name:
You lot. Does anyone remember
how Omulette ended up here?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0017
rows.name: Craa, details escep me!

rows.label: qst202409_msg0018
rows.name: She always been here, craa?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0019
rows.name:
You cannot be serious.
Everyone forgot?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0027
rows.name: Wow, that's a pretty shiny rock.

rows.label: qst202409_msg0028
rows.name:
It piece of Bellflower Krystal!
My preciousest treasure, craa!

rows.label: qst202409_msg0029
rows.name: Wow, that's so cool!

rows.label: qst202409_msg0030
rows.name:
IBUKI!
Are you even listening?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0020
rows.name:
Oh, uh... Well that solves the
mystery of whatever we were
doing! Time to go home!

rows.label: qst202409_msg0021
rows.name:
No no no, what we were doing
is trying to bring the countess
back to her home, remember?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0022
rows.name: What, really?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0023
rows.name:
Me go home?
Where home is?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0024
rows.name:
Countess Omulette. The King is
searching for you, so would you
accompany us back to your home?

rows.label: qst202409_msg0025
rows.name:
Father lookink for me?
OK, craa! I go with you!

rows.label: qst202409_msg0026
rows.name:
Yay! Follow me, I'll get you
back safely to Torigo.

rows.label: qst202409_msg0031
rows.name: *sigh* It's Avaritia.
